			<Text>+1 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Produksi dari Tambang di atas sumber daya Strategis.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BELIEF_GODDESS_OF_FESTIVALS_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>+1 [ICON_FOOD] Makanan dari [ICON_RESOURCE_WINE] Anggur, [ICON_RESOURCE_INCENSE] Dupa, [ICON_RESOURCE_COCOA] Kakao, [ICON_RESOURCE_TOBACCO] Tembakau, [ICON_RESOURCE_COFFEE] Kopi, dan [ICON_RESOURCE_TEA] Perkebunan Teh.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_BELIEF_ORAL_TRADITION_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>+1 [ICON_CULTURE] Budaya dari [ICON_RESOURCE_BANANAS] Pisang, [ICON_RESOURCE_CITRUS] Jeruk, [ICON_RESOURCE_COTTON] Kapas, [ICON_RESOURCE_DYES] Pewarna, [ICON_RESOURCE_SILK] Sutra, [ICON_RESOURCE_SPICES] Rempah-rempah, dan [ICON_RESOURCE_SUGAR] Perkebunan Gula.</Text>
		</Row>
